{"tid":1506770,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大家唔記得一件重要事：今日圍國泰城！！！","createTime":"2019-08-26T02:05:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T02:53:02.000Z","uid":149021,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef015f9ff6e199ac6a7641e8e101c267cfd062a","tid":1506770,"uid":149021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:05:24.000Z","msg":"大家係咪唔記得左今日圍國泰城 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攬炒巴同佢團隊宣傳左 冇人知？<br />\n我突登請左假 冇人去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出面冇post講既 立即幫我推上熱門！!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">（26/8)，國泰員工同香港人既反擊，抵抗白色恐怖，捍衛人身自由</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">詳情：<br />\n星期一！圍國泰城！<br />\n8月26日星期一下午，還香港打工仔公道！<br />\n<br />\n日期：8月26日(一）<br />\n時間：1300-2100<br />\n地點：機場觀景路國泰城</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">交通：各區可搭E車或東涌站搭S車去</span><br />\n<br />\n利申，攬炒團隊並非主辦單位，謹代「國泰員工致香港人書團隊」宣布行動，幫手集結港人力量<br />\n<br />\n原post link:攬炒巴叫大家星期一入機場啊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1501202\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1501202</a>"},{"pid":"3eb28e9a2ffa4ed7df5bdd335c1a0cb4379fc4bd","tid":1506770,"uid":149021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:05:56.000Z","msg":"自推十連！"},{"pid":"54053dbb7a84157d4713f3ed953b9ba55cb0e088","tid":1506770,"uid":149021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:06:06.000Z","msg":"自推十連！"},{"pid":"a1af1eafb91a2197b9f0dd214f720074553f5ed1","tid":1506770,"uid":163945,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:06:12.000Z","msg":"唔係改到星期三咩？"},{"pid":"dcb87096f7f4d0dda1d1969f27b06cf22c2993d4","tid":1506770,"uid":169079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:06:13.000Z","msg":"屌又話改星期三"},{"pid":"b6b63f48a47a63e6e57ae65a8159c31c8ae842da","tid":1506770,"uid":54326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci