，我方亦已準備好上訴之工作。<br />\n<br />\n4. 請各位留意職工盟之集會安排，留意TG資訊頻道及FACEBOOK專頁。"},{"pid":"706b1f970f7c8d8bfe0a6554fde6ef59ca290d5d","tid":1506770,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:09:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />星期三見啦"},{"pid":"a885e0c8b655d0766a3f7e468609969dbca36280","tid":1506770,"uid":265354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:10:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"357279c59d501bf9cc76512499f4ccf3bb1ff1e5","tid":1506770,"uid":40287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:53:02.000Z","msg":"休息一天吧"}]}